    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a definitive driver\u2019s machine, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Differential Lock. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and lateral grip this chassis is renowned for. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement inspection, ensuring the structural integrity matches the powertrain's output. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp and uncompromised.",
      "price": 36500.0,
